OL,5, The Buddha of Suburbia and My Beautiful
OL,6, Launderette writer Hanif Kureishi has  
OL,7, said he believed he was dying after an 
OL,8, accident in Rome on Boxing Day.        
OL,10,FThe Oscar-nominated scriptwriter and   
OL,11,Fnovelist said his injuries have left   
OL,12,Fhim unable to move his arms or legs.   
OL,14,F"I cannot scratch my nose, make a phone
OL,15,Fcall or feed myself," he said. "As you 
OL,16,Fcan imagine, this is both humiliating, 
OL,17,Fdegrading and a burden for others."    
OL,19,FA spine operation has led to "minor    
OL,20,Fimprovements" in recent days, he said. 
